▸ image_prompt（English only — drives image AI directly; describe environment AND characters）
  MINIMUM LENGTH: At least 100 English words.
  No violent, gory, death-related, or sexually explicit content.

  MANDATORY STRUCTURE (all sections in order, none may be skipped):
    [ArtStyle] → [Composition] → [GroundLayer] → [ForegroundObjectsBlock] → [MidgroundBlock] → [BackgroundBlock] → [LightingBlock] → [AtmosphereBlock] → [CharactersBlock] → [ColorPalette] → [OpticsBlock] → [QualityBoosters]

  COMPOSITION — must match shot_size exactly:
    extreme_close_up → extreme detail of a single object or surface; no wide environment
    close_up          → one primary object or architectural detail fills frame
    medium            → 2-3 environment elements with spatial relationship visible
    wide/extreme_wide → broad landscape or architectural scene, environment dominates frame

  GROUND LAYER — always required, even for interior shots:
    — State the precise ground surface material: cracked clay / polished marble / weathered wood planks /
      wet cobblestone / packed dirt / snow-dusted stone / submerged stone steps / etc.
    — Describe ground-level details: debris scatter, puddle reflections, fallen objects, shadow patterns
    ✅ "cracked grey flagstone floor with displaced tiles at irregular intervals, dust accumulation in joints,
        scattered broken ceramic shards foreground-right"
    ❌ "stone floor" → no depth, AI fills with generic result

  FOREGROUND OBJECTS BLOCK — 1-3 named objects with full physical detail:
    — Each object: name + material + dimensions relative to frame + exact position in frame
    — State how object connects to ground (resting on / embedded in / leaning against / hanging from)
    — Describe surface wear, weathering, or any emitted light/effect
    ✅ "a 1.8m granite stele foreground-center, face angled 20° toward camera, diagonal hairline crack from
        upper-left to mid-face, base 40cm deep in earth, moss creeping 30cm up each side"
    ❌ "a stele" → no spatial anchor, AI places it randomly

  MID-GROUND BLOCK — spatial structure defining depth:
    — 1-3 named structural or natural elements with material and position
    — State relative distances and overlapping relationships
    — Include any openings (archway / doorway / gap / window) that create depth cues
    ✅ "two stone columns flanking a 3m-wide gateway mid-ground-center, left column intact, right column
        sheared at 2m height with jagged fracture, stone lintel partially collapsed"
    ❌ "columns in the background" → no material, no position, no detail

  BACKGROUND BLOCK — atmospheric depth:
    — Name far-field elements (mountain ridge / forest canopy / palace wall / cave ceiling)
    — State sky or ceiling conditions and color
    — Include atmospheric effects with density and extent
    ✅ "dense pine forest canopy at 10m height background, warm amber light filtering through gaps as
        scattered vertical shafts, distant mountain silhouette faint through 20% haze"
    ❌ "forest background" → AI fills randomly

  LIGHTING BLOCK — name source, angle, temperature, AND where shadow falls:
    — Source type: directional sunlight / overcast diffuse / torch / candle / magic glow / moonlight
    — Angle: upper-left / upper-right / top-down / underlit / side-rim
    — Color temperature in Kelvin
    — Shadow description: hard-edged / soft diffused, direction, length, surface they fall on
    ✅ "single directional amber sunlight from upper-right at 35°, 3000K warm cast, casting long hard shadow
        of stele diagonally left-and-down across flagstone, cool blue-grey shadow pooling in recessed areas"
    ❌ "dramatic lighting" → AI picks randomly

  ATMOSPHERE BLOCK — environmental particles and air quality:
    — Describe any suspended particles: dust motes / smoke wisps / fog / rain / ember sparks / pollen
    — State density, drift direction, where they concentrate (in light shafts / near ground / etc.)
    — If no particles: state "clear air, no atmospheric haze" to prevent AI adding random effects

  CHARACTERS BLOCK — describe each character present in the shot using their exact name from 【角色信息】 (omit entirely if no characters):
    — Name: always start with the exact character name. Never use "figure", "young man", "woman", or any appearance-based label as a substitute.
    — Position: where in frame (foreground-center / mid-ground-left / background-right / etc.)
    — Body posture and action: what the character is doing, body orientation, limb positions
    — Facial expression: specific expression (determined gaze / furrowed brow / slight smile / etc.)
    — Clothing silhouette: general style only; no overly specific details that conflict with reference images
    — Spatial relationship to environment: standing on / leaning against / emerging from / etc.
    ✅ "foreground-center: Ling Yun standing upright facing camera, arms at sides, head slightly bowed, expression solemn and still"
    ✅ "mid-ground-left: Bai Xue crouching behind stone pillar, one hand pressed against pillar surface, body angled away from gateway, tense posture"
    ❌ "foreground-center: figure in dark robes..." → replace "figure" with the character's exact name

  OPTICS BLOCK — focal length matched to shot_size:
    extreme_close_up/close_up → "85-100mm f/1.8-2.8, subject razor-sharp, background fully blurred"
    medium                     → "50mm f/4, moderate depth-of-field, background soft but readable"
    wide/extreme_wide          → "24mm f/8, deep focus, sharp from foreground to background"

  QUALITY BOOSTERS — always last, choose by art style:
    Realistic:    "masterpiece, best quality, ultra-detailed, 8k uhd, sharp focus, photorealistic, cinematic lighting"
    Anime/illust: "masterpiece, best quality, ultra-detailed, vibrant colors, clean linework, professional illustration"

  PRE-SUBMIT CHECKLIST (verify each before writing the field):
    □ Characters described by exact name (not "figure"); position, posture, expression included if present; omitted if no characters in shot
    □ Word count ≥ 100 words
    □ Ground surface material and detail stated
    □ 1-3 foreground objects with exact position, material, dimensions stated
    □ Mid-ground structural elements with spatial relationships stated
    □ Background depth elements and atmosphere stated
    □ Lighting: source type + angle + color temperature + shadow direction and surface all stated
    □ Atmospheric particles described (or explicitly stated as absent)
    □ Focal length stated and matches shot_size
    □ Quality boosters at the very end

{% else %}
▸ image_prompt（图片生成专用提示词——描述环境场景和角色）
  最低字数：不少于100字。
  ⚠️ 严禁出现暴力、血腥、伤亡、色情相关敏感词。

  强制结构（所有区块按顺序拼接，不得跳过任何一个）：
    [画风] → [构图] → [地面层] → [前景物件区块] → [中景区块] → [背景区块] → [光线区块] → [大气区块] → [角色区块] → [色调] → [镜头参数] → [画质词]

  构图——必须与 shot_size 字段精确对应：
    extreme_close_up → 单件物体或单一表面极致细节特写
    close_up          → 一个主体物件或建筑细节占满画框
    medium            → 2-3个环境元素，空间关系清晰可见
    wide/extreme_wide → 广阔景观或建筑场景，环境主导画面

  地面层——必填，室内室外均适用：
    — 精确描述地面材质：龟裂荒土/大理石抛光/风化木板/湿润石板/压实泥土/积雪石面/水下石阶等
    — 地面级细节：碎片散布、水坑反射、倒伏物体、投影图案
    ✅ "前景灰色不规则碎石板地面，多处石板错位移动，石缝积尘，右前景散落破碎陶器碎片"
    ❌ "石板地面" → 无纵深，AI随机填充

  前景物件区块——1-3个命名物体，配完整物理细节：
    — 每件物体：名称+材质+相对画框尺寸+精确位置
    — 说明物体如何与地面连接（置于/嵌入/倚靠/悬挂于）
    — 描述表面磨损、风化状态，或发出的光效
    ✅ "前景居中约1.8米高花岗岩石碑，碑面斜20度朝向镜头，从左上至中部有发丝宽斜向裂缝，底部
        40厘米嵌入地面，碑身两侧苔藓向上蔓延约30厘米"
    ❌ "一块石碑" → 无空间定位，AI随机放置

  中景区块——构建纵深的空间结构：
    — 1-3个命名结构或自然元素，说明材质和画框位置
    — 描述相对距离和叠压关系
    — 包含任何制造纵深线索的开口（拱门/门洞/缺口/窗口）
    ✅ "中景居中两根石柱夹持约3米宽门洞，左柱完好，右柱在2米高处被齐断，断口参差不齐，横梁
        石架部分坍塌"
    ❌ "背景有柱子" → 无材质、无位置、无细节

  背景区块——大气纵深：
    — 命名远景元素（山脊/森林树冠/宫墙/洞穴顶壁）
    — 描述天空或顶部状态及色彩
    — 包含大气效果，说明密度和范围
    ✅ "背景10米高松林树冠，暖琥珀光从间隙中以垂直光柱形式透射而下，远处山脊在20%能见度薄雾
        中隐约可见"
    ❌ "森林背景" → AI随机填充

  光线区块——命名光源、角度、色温，并说明阴影投向：
    — 光源类型：定向阳光/阴天散射/火炬/烛火/魔法光效/月光
    — 角度：左上方/右上方/顶部正射/仰角底光/侧逆光
    — 色温（开尔文值）
    — 阴影描述：硬边/柔和漫射，投向，长度，落在哪个地面材质上
    ✅ "右上方约35度单一琥珀色阳光，色温3000K，将石碑硬边阴影斜向投射至左下方石板地面，
        凹陷区域积聚冷蓝灰色阴影"
    ❌ "戏剧性光线" → AI随机发挥，结果不稳定

  大气区块——环境粒子与空气质感：
    — 描述悬浮粒子：尘埃浮粒/烟雾/薄雾/降雨/火星/花粉/光尘
    — 说明密度、漂移方向、集中区域（光柱中/近地面/etc.）
    — 若无粒子：明确写"空气清透，无大气薄雾"，防止AI随机添加

  角色区块——描述画面中出现的每位角色，必须使用【角色信息】中的精确名称（若无角色则省略此区块）：
    — 名称：必须以角色精确名称开头。禁止用"人影"、"他"/"她"、"少年"、"女子"等代替角色名
    — 画面位置：在画框中的位置（前景居中/中景偏左/背景右侧等）
    — 身体姿态与动作：角色正在做什么，身体朝向，肢体位置
    — 面部表情：具体表情（坚定的目光/微皱的眉头/淡淡的微笑等）
    — 服装轮廓：服装风格和色调（避免过于细节化，以免与参考图冲突）
    — 与环境的空间关系：站立于/倚靠在/从……中走出/蹲伏于等
    ✅ "前景居中：凌云直立面向镜头，双臂垂于身侧，头微微低垂，神情肃穆"
    ✅ "中景偏左：白雪蹲伏于石柱后方，一手按住柱面，身体背向门洞，姿态紧绷"
    ❌ "前景居中：身着深色长袍的人影直立..." → 用精确角色名，改为"凌云直立..."

  镜头参数——焦距必须与 shot_size 对应：
    extreme_close_up/close_up → "85-100mm，f/1.8-2.8，主体极清晰，背景完全虚化"
    medium                     → "50mm，f/4，适中景深，背景柔焦可辨"
    wide/extreme_wide          → "24mm，f/8，全域清晰，前景到背景均锐利"

  画质词——附在最末尾，根据画风选一：
    写实风：  "masterpiece, best quality, ultra-detailed, 8k uhd, sharp focus, photorealistic, cinematic lighting"
    动漫/插画："masterpiece, best quality, ultra-detailed, vibrant colors, clean linework, professional illustration"

  输出前自检清单（每条验证后再写字段）：
    □ 若有角色出场：已使用精确角色名称（非"人影"）描述位置、姿态、表情；若无角色则省略角色区块
    □ 字数不少于100字
    □ 地面材质和细节已说明
    □ 1-3件前景物体的精确位置、材质、尺寸已说明
    □ 中景结构元素和空间关系已说明
    □ 背景纵深元素和大气效果已说明
    □ 光线：光源类型+角度+色温+阴影方向及落地材质 均已说明
    □ 大气粒子已描述（或明确标注为无）
    □ 焦距已标注且与景别对应
    □ 画质词在最末尾

{% endif %}
